    "description": "起初 <strong>俄罗斯赛跑者 </strong>，在其中您必须发现自己处于穷人的境地 <strong>小猪</strong>, 逃离 <strong>有议程的军事委员</strong>. 不要让军委追上你，否则你就得 <strong>签署议程 </strong>或者 <strong>进监狱 </strong>但是，您总是可以同意。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251380/extras/388b8e26fdaabdfdf737926c7de2e804.poster.avif?t=1749477382\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251380/extras/388b8e26fdaabdfdf737926c7de2e804.webm?t=1749477382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251380/extras/388b8e26fdaabdfdf737926c7de2e804.mp4?t=1749477382\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>无限生成的世界 </strong>，因为俄罗斯的边界在任何地方都没有尽头</li><li> <strong>大气位置 </strong>，反映真实的俄罗斯腹地，路上不掉坑</li><li> <strong>拖拉机 </strong>和 <strong>其他车辆 </strong>那个借来的Piglet会让你有时候跑不动</li><li> <strong>很多项目 </strong>这有助于这场艰难的比赛</li><li> <strong>皇帝像钱币 </strong>，需要在比赛中收集升级物品和贿赂军事委员</li><li> <strong>排行榜 </strong>与最成功的逃避者（数据将转移到俄罗斯联邦国防部）</li><li> <strong>爱国音乐 </strong>，你必须站着玩</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251380/extras/871d6b2ad822070d19c97e247be7317a.poster.avif?t=1749477382\" width=610 height=343 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251380/extras/871d6b2ad822070d19c97e247be7317a.webm?t=1749477382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251380/extras/133db20a5221b506865c2a6aa7d46d9e.poster.avif?t=1749477382\" width=604 height=50 ><source src=\"https://shar